---
const {} = Astro.props;
---

<video class="hero-video" autoplay muted loop>
  <source src="" type="video/mp4" />
  Your browser does not support the video tag.
</video>

<h2>Skil dig ud fra de andre på gaden</h2>

<sektion class="hero__content">
  <p class="hero_tekst">Pleasant lancerer en ny kollektion, der garanterer, at du skiller dig ud fra mængden. Hver style er upcyclet af glemte tekstiler og bærer på sin helt egen historie.</p>

  <p class="hero_tekst">Vi ønsker at give hvert item nyt liv ved at lade det blive en del af din historie. Bliv one of a kind med vores nye, helt unikke styles, der afspejler præcis, hvem du er.</p>
</sektion>

<sektion class="billeder_3">
  <img src="/images/vaskeri.jpeg" alt="hero" class="vaskeri" />
  <div>
    <img src="/images/drenge.jpg" alt="hero" class="drenge" />
    <a href="/listeview">
      <button>Se Kollektion</button>
    </a>
  </div>
  <img src="/images/henrikcap.jpg" alt="hero" class="henrikcap" />
</sektion>

<img src="/images/citat.png" alt="citat" class="catchphrase" />

<style>
  .catchphrase {
    width: 100%;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .hero-video {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    text-align: left;
    padding: 1rem;
    color: #333;
    font-family: "new-spirit", serif;
  }
  h3 {
    font-family: "new-spirit", serif;
  }
  .hero__content {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8rem;

    width: 100%;

    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 100px;
  }

  .hero_tekst {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: #333;
    font-family: "new-spirit", serif;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding: 1rem;
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  .billeder_3 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    width: 100%;
    align-items: center;
    justify-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .vaskeri {
    width: 70%;
    height: 65%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 5px solid #f5b980;
  }
  .drenge {
    width: 80%;
    height: 80%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 5px solid #a2412e;
  }
  .henrikcap {
    width: 70%;
    height: 65%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 5px solid #88beac;
  }
  button {
    color: black;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: solid 1px black;
    font-family: "new-spirit", serif;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .hero__content {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 100px;
    }

    .hero_tekst {
      max-width: 700px;
    }

    .billeder_3 {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .vaskeri {
      width: 70%;
      height: 65%;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 5px solid #f5b980;
    }
    .drenge {
      width: 80%;
      height: 80%;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 5px solid #a2412e;
    }
    .henrikcap {
      width: 70%;
      height: 65%;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 5px solid #88beac;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
